      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:400;color:#f0ece4;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Floor Plans, Site Plans, and Building Drawings: What Brisbane Sellers Should Provide to Buyers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Serious buyers study plans more than almost any marketing asset except photos. Here is what each plan actually shows, what they cost, and which ones every Brisbane seller should provide.
      </p>
    </div>
